markets.title: Will Boston have a Michelin star restaurant in 2025?
markets.rules_primary: If there is a Michelin Guide for 2025 that includes a restauarant in Boston that has earned at least one Michelin star, then the market resolves to Yes.
markets.rules_secondary: A restaurant need not be located within the formal city limits of <city> to qualify for the Payout Criterion, provided that it is listed in a Michelin Guide associated with <city>.
markets.early_close_condition: This market will close and expire after the year's Michelin Guides are released.
